OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1779725464
OL,3,CMan who died in Enniskillen crash
OL,4,Cnamed as 39-year-old Cavan man
OL,6,FA man has died following a single-
OL,7,Fvehicle collision in Enniskillen on
OL,8,FSunday 24 May.
OL,10,FHe was Michael Kenna from the
OL,11,FBelturbet area in Co Cavan.
OL,13,FThe crash, involving a motorcycle,
OL,14,Fhappened around 6am in the Marble Arch
OL,15,FRoad area of Florencecourt.
OL,17,FEmergency services attended but the 39-
OL,18,Fyear-old was pronounced dead at the
OL,19,Fscene.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
