FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1779725464
OL,3,CMan who died in Enniskillen crash
OL,4,Cnamed as 39-year-old Cavan man
OL,6,FThe road which was closed for a time
OL,7,Fhas since reopened.
OL,9,FLocal UUP Councillor Mark Ovens said:
OL,10,F"Sadly, this is yet another tragic
OL,11,Freminder of the dangers that exist on
OL,12,Fmany of our rural roads ....
OL,14,F"... It is especially heartbreaking
OL,15,Fthat this tragedy has happened over a
OL,16,Fbank holiday weekend, a time when
OL,17,Ffamilies should be together, not
OL,18,Ffacing unimaginable loss.
OL,26,@rD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1779725464
OL,3,CMan who died in Enniskillen crash
OL,4,Cnamed as 39-year-old Cavan man
OL,6,F"I would also pay tribute to the
OL,7,Femergency services who attended the
OL,8,Fscene in very difficult circumstances.
OL,10,F"I would urge anyone travelling over
OL,11,Fthe remainder of the weekend to take
OL,12,Fextra care on the roads. Far too many
OL,13,Ffamilies across Northern Ireland have
OL,14,Falready had their lives changed
OL,15,Fforever by road traffic collisions
OL,16,Fthis year."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@KO]
