OL,3,CMan who died in Enniskillen crash
OL,4,Cnamed as 39-year-old Cavan man
OL,6,FA PSNI spokesperson said: "Police
OL,7,Freceived a report at around 6am of a
OL,8,Fcollision involving a motorcycle in
OL,9,Fthe Marble Arch Road area of
OL,10,FFlorencecourt," said Detective
OL,11,FInspector Dave Stewart, from the
OL,12,FCollision Investigation Unit.
OL,14,F"Officers, along with colleagues from
OL,15,Fthe Northern Ireland Ambulance Service
OL,16,Fand Northern Ireland Fire and Rescue
OL,17,FService, attended, however, sadly
OL,18,FMichael was pronounced deceased at the
OL,19,Fscene.
OL,26,@nD@[OUrD@OO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
