CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1779725464
OL,3,CMan who died in Enniskillen crash
OL,4,Cnamed as 39-year-old Cavan man
OL,6,F"The Marble Arch Road, which was
OL,7,Fclosed for a time, has since reopened.
OL,9,F"Our inquiries are continuing and we
OL,10,Fwould appeal to anyone who witnessed
OL,11,Fthe collision, or who may have any
OL,12,Finformation which could assist with
OL,13,Four investigation ` including dashcam
OL,14,For other footage ` contact the
OL,15,FCollision Investigation Unit on 101."
